      "type": "message",
      "text": "Here’s my list of VCV Rack plugins (<https://vcvrack.com/plugins.html>) that use some kind of programming-ish approach:\n<https://github.com/Rcomian/jsfx-vcv> - Reaper JSFX language embedded\n<https://github.com/david-c14/Torpedo> - a “modem device” :open_mouth:\n<https://github.com/bokontep/BokontepByteBeatMachine> - JS bytecode\n<https://github.com/FrankBuss/Formula> - fork of above\n<https://github.com/freddyz/computerscare-vcv-modules> - crazy madness",
